    "(c) SLIM system.",
    "The 4D data cube of \"x + y + z + 𝜆\" is decoupled into multi-view aliased information through modulation of the metalens array and captured by the camera.Finally, the spectral reconstruction algorithm and super-resolution module proposed in the article are used to achieve 4D imaging.",
